        <updateDate>2013-07-29T19:46:52Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Permits the continued operation of trucks on any segment of U.S. Route 78 in Mississippi designated as a route on the Interstate System. Prohibits federal weight limitation requirements from applying to those trucks that could operate legally on such segment before that designation.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
